{"tid":239501,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"去東京12天點玩好","createTime":"2017-05-11T17:07:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T10:46:04.000Z","uid":68675,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"86638561c083ac32e43d161bd6b5861448d927d1","tid":239501,"uid":68675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T17:07:07.000Z","msg":"行程點樣安排好呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有d咩地方係值得去？<br />\n有咩必食必買必玩？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第一天<br />\n16:25落機<br />\n👉🏻玩咩好？<br />\n<br />\n❤️第二天<br />\n👉🏻天上山纜車<br />\n👉🏻富士急樂園<br />\n👉🏻浸溫泉<br />\n<br />\n❤️第三天<br />\n👉🏻音樂小鎮<br />\n👉🏻 Outlet<br />\n👉🏻返新宿玩<br />\n<br />\n❤️第四天<br />\n👉🏻表參道<br />\n👉🏻原宿<br />\n👉🏻竹下通<br />\n👉🏻明治神宮<br />\n👉🏻涉谷<br />\n<br />\n❤️第五天<br />\n👉🏻築地市場<br />\n👉🏻銀座<br />\n👉🏻台場<br />\n👉🏻秋葉原<br />\n<br />\n❤️第六天<br />\n👉🏻淺草和服<br />\n👉🏻晴空塔<br />\n👉🏻有咩附近公園可以去下？<br />\n<br />\n❤️第七天<br />\n👉🏻玩咩好？<br />\n<br />\n❤️第八天<br />\n👉🏻海洋迪士尼<br />\n<br />\n❤️第九天<br />\n👉🏻迪士尼<br />\n<br />\n❤️第十天<br />\n👉🏻玩咩好？<br />\n<br />\n❤️第十一天<br />\n👉🏻玩咩好？<br />\n<br />\n❤️第十二天<br />\n👉🏻玩咩好？<br />\n👉🏻19:15要飛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求意見謝謝！"},{"pid":"d53bc59c71685745b0fae87c23170b027e38d297","tid":239501,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T17:13:32.000Z","msg":"川越丶鎌倉丶日光"},{"pid":"400f33163de9f0987abf4c34e81e1e39850e8eb1","tid":239501,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T17:15:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>川越丶鎌倉丶日光</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n川越有啲失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9168a85a8392b510141a7f231142baabfd110d67","tid":239501,"uid":2997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T18:03:04.000Z","msg":"下星期去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hk