0baf4702cdf479e0bf772bac5d8e826a7bac9","tid":239501,"uid":50980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T12:34:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>6月到7月 海洋個胡迪維修，<br />\n具體時間忘記左，大家上官網睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩岩睇左 6月23號先維修完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗緊為唔為左佢改行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實唔知好唔好玩  因為得哩個位係toy story 主題   老實講就咁睇香港個toy story area 仲吸引過日本個  仲要人多到爆炸  fast pass 我上次去上午就攞哂  之後要排200min. 所以都唔知好唔好玩  如果排咁耐唔好玩 失落感會好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df3fd516cefe22522cda3a941828b0ba39cb269a","tid":239501,"uid":25952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T13:29:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>6月到7月 海洋個胡迪維修，<br />\n具體時間忘記左，大家上官網睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩岩睇左 6月23號先維修完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗緊為唔為左佢改行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實唔知好唔好玩  因為得哩個位係toy story 主題   老實講就咁睇香港個toy story area 仲吸引過日本個  仲要人多到爆炸  fast pass 我上次去上午就攞哂  之後要排200min. 所以都唔知好唔好玩  如果排咁耐唔好玩 失落感會好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n海洋個胡迪同香港迪士尼其中一隻射擊game好似<br />\n吸引度唔大 <br />\n反而火山入面個兩個機動遊戲就真係讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢兩個係必玩"},{"pid":"13f60d1ccc7277634826d19e9fc39bd038716803","tid":239501,"uid":60371,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T13:43:04.000Z","msg":"去淺草著和服千奇唔好比錢人幫你影相 個陣比左5000yen 勁伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b99827cca945c7509c1d9d71e4348ddee2bb965c","tid":239501,"uid":6767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T13:52:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>6月到7月 海洋個胡迪維修，<br />\n具體時間忘記左，大家上官網睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩岩睇左 6月23號先維修完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗緊為唔為左佢改行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實唔知好唔好玩  因為得哩個位係toy story 主題   老實講就咁睇香港個toy story area 仲吸引過日本個  仲要人多到爆炸  fast pass 我上次去上午就攞哂  之後要排200min. 所以都唔知好唔好玩  如果排咁耐唔好玩 失落感會好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n海洋個胡迪同香港迪士尼其中一隻射擊game好似<br />\n吸引度唔大 <br />\n反而火山入面個兩個機動遊戲就真係讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢兩個係必玩</blockquote><br />\n本身好中意toystory<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以決定改行程過左23號先去玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你講火山果個係咪地心探險之旅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係既話我改左日子呢個又無得玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7998dbb97a6999202b7fdf34730298c99e23e5bf","tid":239501,"uid":49952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T02:24:17.000Z","msg":"我都6月 去呀， 無toy story我地都唔去Disney 啦，宜家係諗緊6月中去河口湖 個富士山會唔會無景 雪溶變禿山"}]}